name: "Tattoos without ink" by Cinthia Ponce
description:
I don't have time to heal my new scars.
This whole scar is somehow like a tattoo.
I have more tattoos without ink than with ink. 

I will show them all and even on the days I feel like throwing up my words.
No matter what happens
I don't care, let it go, even if I fall, even if I fall.


Image source: pexels Intervention, customization and collage of images. Conceptual art. With different editing tools
